        <abstract> 
<p>Will inform all foreign publishers that John Murray will supply 1000 copies of heliotype plates [for <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>] for £75. CD would not have used so many photos had he foreseen the cost, but woodcuts would not have done.</p> 
        </abstract>
